{"title":"How to use Xi-editor?","date":"2019-05-08T06:38:05.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 8, 2019","L":"05/08/2019","MM-DD":"05-08"},"link":"2019/05/08/How-to-use-Xi-editor","tags":["Rust"],"updated":"2021-01-30T07:14:12.065Z","content":"<img src=\"/2019/05/08/How-to-use-Xi-editor/xi-mac.png\" class=\"\" title=\"xi-mac\">\n<h1 id=\"what-is-xi-editor?\">What is Xi-editor?<a title=\"#what-is-xi-editor?\" href=\"#what-is-xi-editor?\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>The xi-editor project is an attempt to build a high quality text editor, using modern software engineering techniques.</strong></p>\n<h1 id=\"install-it-on-macos\">Install it on macOS<a title=\"#install-it-on-macos\" href=\"#install-it-on-macos\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"requirements\">Requirements<a title=\"#requirements\" href=\"#requirements\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Xcode 10.2</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Rust</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"installing\">Installing<a title=\"#installing\" href=\"#installing\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"clone-the-repository:\">Clone the repository:<a title=\"#clone-the-repository:\" href=\"#clone-the-repository:\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> --recurse-submodules https://github.com/xi-editor/xi-mac</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> xi-mac</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"build-and-open:\">Build and Open:<a title=\"#build-and-open:\" href=\"#build-and-open:\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">xcodebuild</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>XiEditor.app</code> in <code>./build/Release/</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"move-to-applications-folder:\">Move to Applications Folder:<a title=\"#move-to-applications-folder:\" href=\"#move-to-applications-folder:\"></a></h3>\n<p>drag to Application folder</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cp -r Build/Release/XiEditor.app /Applications</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"cli\">CLI<a title=\"#cli\" href=\"#cli\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"installing-1\">installing<a title=\"#installing-1\" href=\"#installing-1\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Open XiEditor</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>XiEditor &gt; Install Command Line Tool</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"install-theme\">Install theme<a title=\"#install-theme\" href=\"#install-theme\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"download-theme-file\">Download theme file<a title=\"#download-theme-file\" href=\"#download-theme-file\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/dracula/sublime/archive/master.zip\" target=\"_blank\">dracula for sublime</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"move-to-:\">Move to :<a title=\"#move-to-:\" href=\"#move-to-:\"></a></h2>\n<p>find <code>/Users/username/Library/Application\\ Support/XiEditor/themes/</code></p>\n<p>drag <code>Dracula.tmTheme</code> to it</p>\n<h2 id=\"change-theme\">Change theme<a title=\"#change-theme\" href=\"#change-theme\"></a></h2>\n<p>A theme can be selected from the Debug &gt; Theme menu. There is not yet a mechanism for including custom themes.</p>\n<h1 id=\"configuration\">Configuration<a title=\"#configuration\" href=\"#configuration\"></a></h1>\n<p>the general preferences are located at ~/Library/Application Support/XiEditor/preferences.xiconfig. This file can be opened from File &gt; Preferences (⌘ + ,).</p>\n<h1 id=\"install-plugin\">Install plugin<a title=\"#install-plugin\" href=\"#install-plugin\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"download-plugin\">Download plugin<a title=\"#download-plugin\" href=\"#download-plugin\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/scholtzan/xi-word-count.git\" target=\"_blank\">Word Count Plugin</a> for Xi-editor</p>\n<h2 id=\"installation\">Installation<a title=\"#installation\" href=\"#installation\"></a></h2>\n<p>unzip <code>/Users/huixie/Library/Application\\ Support/XiEditor/plugins/</code></p>\n<p>drag xi-mac folder to it</p>\n<p>go to plugin folder</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>open Xi-editor，Debug &gt; Plugin start</p>\n<img src=\"/2019/05/08/How-to-use-Xi-editor/word_count_plugin.png\" class=\"\" title=\"word_count_plugin\">\n<h2 id=\"other-plugin\">Other plugin<a title=\"#other-plugin\" href=\"#other-plugin\"></a></h2>\n<p>Search <a href=\"https://github.com/search?q=xi-editor+plugin\" target=\"_blank\">xi-editor plugin</a> in Github.</p>\n","prev":{"title":"The Tiny Compiler","link":"2019/10/08/The-Tiny-Compiler"},"plink":"https://syaki.github.io/2019/05/08/How-to-use-Xi-editor/","toc":[{"id":"what-is-xi-editor?","title":"What is Xi-editor?","index":"1"},{"id":"install-it-on-macos","title":"Install it on macOS","index":"2","children":[{"id":"requirements","title":"Requirements","index":"2.1"},{"id":"installing","title":"Installing","index":"2.2","children":[{"id":"clone-the-repository:","title":"Clone the repository:","index":"2.2.1"},{"id":"build-and-open:","title":"Build and Open:","index":"2.2.2"},{"id":"move-to-applications-folder:","title":"Move to Applications Folder:","index":"2.2.3"}]}]},{"id":"cli","title":"CLI","index":"3","children":[{"id":"installing-1","title":"installing","index":"3.1"}]},{"id":"install-theme","title":"Install theme","index":"4","children":[{"id":"download-theme-file","title":"Download theme file","index":"4.1"},{"id":"move-to-:","title":"Move to :","index":"4.2"},{"id":"change-theme","title":"Change theme","index":"4.3"}]},{"id":"configuration","title":"Configuration","index":"5"},{"id":"install-plugin","title":"Install plugin","index":"6","children":[{"id":"download-plugin","title":"Download plugin","index":"6.1"},{"id":"installation","title":"Installation","index":"6.2"},{"id":"other-plugin","title":"Other plugin","index":"6.3"}]}],"copyright":{"author":"Syaki","link":"<a href=\"https://syaki.github.io/2019/05/08/How-to-use-Xi-editor/\" title=\"How to use Xi-editor?\">https://syaki.github.io/2019/05/08/How-to-use-Xi-editor/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}